message.body: Do you have any plans for tomorrow night? If not, would you like to go see the Flyers game with me? I have free tix coming my way.
Would love to go! Free ##### time is the best :)
And hockey! Don't forget free hockey too! So glad you can make it!
When do you want to leave? I assume we'll take the subway?
Def the subway. I don't have the tix yet and didn't look up the game start. Let me check....
Game starts at 7. Want to leave my place around 6:15?
Works for me. We'll probably miss a few minutes but that's fine with me
We could go at 6 too. Actually we should prob plan for 6 as I'm usually running a lil late.
I hope it's a decent game. This is not their best season.
No it isn't, but we'll have fun anyway!
